msgid ""
"Administrators can learn more on the `placetel CTI` integration page. Agents "
"can learn more about this function on this page: :doc:`/extras/caller-log`"
msgstr ""

#: ../basics/zammad-glossary.rst:490
msgid ""
"Every ticket gets assigned a priority. By default, the priority is 2 "
"(normal). But it can be changed to either 1 (low) or 3 (high)."
