#: ../extras/two-factor-authentication/security-keys-setup.rst:None
msgid "Editing Security Keys"
msgstr ""

#: ../extras/two-factor-authentication/security-keys-setup.rst:52
msgid ""
"Once set up, security keys can be managed by choosing **Edit** action next "
"to the two-factor authentication method."
msgstr ""

#: ../extras/two-factor-authentication/security-keys-setup.rst:55
msgid ""
"You have an option to remove a key or set up additional ones. There is no "
"limit in number of security keys you can set up, but keep in mind you cannot "
"register an already registered key for your account."
